表的代码预览需要

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('need') and o.name = 'FK_NEED_NEED_MEDICINE')
alter table need
drop constraint FK_NEED_NEED_MEDICINE
go

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('need') and o.name = 'FK_NEED_NEED2_PATIENT')
alter table need
drop constraint FK_NEED_NEED2_PATIENT
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('need')
and name = 'need2_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index need.need2_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('need')
and name = 'need_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index need.need_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('need')
and type = 'U')
drop table need
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: need */
/*==============================================================*/
create table need (
mno char(10) not null,
pno char(8) not null,
constraint PK_NEED primary key nonclustered (mno, pno)
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: need_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index need_FK on need (
mno ASC
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: need2_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index need2_FK on need (
pno ASC
)
go

alter table need
add constraint FK_NEED_NEED_MEDICINE foreign key (mno)
references medicine (mno)
go

alter table need
add constraint FK_NEED_NEED2_PATIENT foreign key (pno)
references patient (pno)
go
